task.summary: Lay out the basic templating structure to extend from
Basic auth implemented. * Authenticate using POST to api/authenticate with params email, password * Add token or set Authorization header in all request having middleware jwt.auth

Implemented: - Registration routes, view and controller - Registration config middleware, that checks if `my_config.allow_registration` is true to let it go through - Use of Elixir to concat and minimize css and js
Implemented: - Email verification. Added confirmated, confirmation_sent (is a datetime) and confirmation_code. - 12 hours allowed since confirmation_sent datetime.
